        </div>
      </div>

      <p style="text-align:center;margin-top:1.5rem;font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--muted);">Not sure? Call us and we will tell you honestly whether it is an emergency or can wait. <a href="tel:07399676656" style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;">07399 676656</a></p>
